<normalizedToken originalValue="Lindroth’s">Lindroth's</normalizedToken>
(1961a: 88-90) monograph on the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="127" pageNumber="128" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Carabidae</taxonomicName>
of Canada and Alaska.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
